Package com.taco.suit_lady.view._nonimported

Class FXMainController

java.lang.Object
com.taco.suit_lady.view._nonimported.FXMainController
@Component @FxmlView("MainView.fxml") public class FXMainController extends Object

The main controller for this JavaFX Application.


- The main controller is responsible for containing, monitoring, and ensuring proper functionality of all JFX-related functionalities of the application.

- In addition to standard JavaFX Controller functionality, the main controller is responsible for FxWeaver and Spring implementation and integration.

    • initialize_BaWT

      private void initialize_BaWT()

      Contains BaWT (Bell and Whistle Test) initialization code.


      Note: Production-level runtime functionality should *never* depend on BaWT code.
      In other words, production-level functionality should be unaffected should all BaWT implementation be removed.
